Dubai
My client, a successful fashion retail leader in the Middle East is seeking talented Merchandise Managers and Head of Merchandising candidates to join them.
An exceptional opportunity to relocate and change your lifestyle!
With a tax-free salary and excellent relocation package for your self and your family it makes it an offer you cant refuse.
You will need to be currently operating at this level within a fashion business. Fast Fashion experience within a blue-chip organisation is preferred.
Salary is dependent on level, up to £100k.
